{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "You're going to get-- those-- those little things I remember and how you recall later on this cousin unfortunately never made it through the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were in the open ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "I actually liked the open ghetto very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "They put us into one big-- big room at a section of town, which was around a big market.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "They called it a market in Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Most of the medieval towns had marketplaces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "It's like a cobblestone area, which was a circle, and around this circle there were houses built.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And that circle was quite large, because all the wagons from the neighboring farms used to come and sell their goods and-- and-- and practice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "But naturally, when we were put in that ghetto no more carts came, and no more goods were being sold in that marketplace.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put us in one of the rooms in one of the buildings around that place, and-- and we-- I had a chance to be with everybody together.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it seemed like there wasn't too much going on, so everybody was home, and I had the attention that I really needed, I guess.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got to sleep with my sisters, and I got to be with everybody all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could sleep wherever I wanted, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only bad thing, they really didn't want to sleep with them, because I-- I-- I was still wetting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did that throughout the whole war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, it-- it came back to me, because I was scared all the time, and I-- I hardly slept through a night without wetting.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
